bum/the-fruits-single/1452959121|title=The Fruits - Single by Col3trane, DJDS & RAYE on Apple Music|work=iTunes Store (UK)|accessdate=7 March 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2019\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"5\" {{TBA}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Love Me Again\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(solo or with [[Jess Glynne]])</span><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B0Y78aVAxod/|title=\ud83d\udc942.8.19\ud83d\udc94|via=[[Instagram]]|date=26 July 2019|accessdate=27 July 2019}}</ref>\n| 55 || 34 || 38\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Make It to Heaven]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with David Guetta and [[Morten Breum|Morten]])</span>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Please Don't Touch\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/please-dont-touch-single/1489662404|title=Please Don't Touch \u2013 Single by Raye|website=Apple Music|accessdate=13 December 2019}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"All of My Love\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Young Adz]])</span><ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/all-of-my-love-feat-young-adz-single/1495858069|title=All Of My Love (feat. Young Adz) - Single by RAYE|website=Apple Music|accessdate=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2020\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Tequila (Jax Jones, Martin Solveig and Raye song)|Tequila]]\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Jax Jones]] and [[Martin Solveig]])</span>\n| 21 || 23<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/irish-singles-chart/20200417/ie7501|title=Official Irish Singles Chart Top 50|publisher=Official Charts Company|date=17 April 2020|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref> || 19\n|\n|''Europa''\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n===As featured artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-